: gumbel-random-float ( loc scale -- n )
    <gumbel-distribution> random ;

TUPLE: logistic-distribution loc scale ;
C: <logistic-distribution> logistic-distribution
M: logistic-distribution random*
    [ [ loc>> ] [ scale>> ] bi ] [ random-unit* ] bi*
