TUPLE: power-distribution alpha ;
C: <power-distribution> power-distribution
M: power-distribution random*
    [ alpha>> ] [ random-unit* log e^ 1 swap - ] bi*
    swap recip ^ ;

: power-random-float ( alpha -- n )
